item.title: CVE-2017-16165|2024-08-05T20:20:05.002Z -- hackerone -- calmquist.static-server%20node%20module
item.description: calmquist.static-server is a static file server. calmquist.static-server is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url.
